    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <h2>Whole House Rewiring FAQs</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How do I know if my house needs rewiring?</h3>
          <p>Signs include: frequent circuit breaker trips, flickering lights, outlets that don't work, burning smells, old two-prong outlets, visible knob & tube or aluminum wiring, and homes built before 1960. We provide free assessments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I live in my home during rewiring?</h3>
